summary: This document is a forwarded email chain from April 2011 showing a failed email delivery attempt to 'jeevacation@gmail.com' and a subsequent forwarded message intended for recipients JE and G Max. The forwarded message contains an attachment titled 'My_Own_Words.docx' and is marked as a privileged and confidential communication.

persons.name: G Max
persons.context: Appears as an additional intended recipient (alongside JE) of a forwarded email containing a confidential document. The email address gmaxl@ellmax.com is associated.

connections.description: Both are listed as recipients of the same confidential email communication containing the document 'My_Own_Words.docx'.

events.title: Failed email delivery attempt
events.description: An email sent to jeevacation@gmail.com was returned with a 'User unknown' error by the mail server postoffice.ftc.naproperties.com.

events.title: Forwarding of confidential document
events.description: A message with the subject 'My Own Words' and an attachment 'My_Own_Words.docx' was forwarded to JE and G Max. The message is marked as a privileged and confidential communication.

keyFacts: An email to 'jeevacation@gmail.com' (associated with JE) failed to deliver on April 27, 2011, with a 'User unknown' error.
A separate email containing the document 'My_Own_Words.docx' was forwarded to JE and G Max on the same day, marked as privileged and confidential.
The communication claims protection under the Electronic Communications Privacy Act (18 USC §§ 2510-2521).
